Scripts  consuming the WP-API from Milne Library News & Events WordPress site http://news.milne-library.org

For: MILNE LIBRARY WEBSITE 
Practical application:  Milne Library blog feed to be displayed on Milne Library Drupal home page https://www.geneseo.edu/library
Benefits:  
1) Eliminates staff time being wasted entering content and uploading media in two different locations
2) Automatic updates of news and events
3) Staff do not have to resize and edit images to display properly within the Drupal page slider
4) Eliminates potential for  mistakes and 'page borking' due to html and styling within the Drupal WYSIWIG editor
5) Eliminates using the Drupal WYSIWIG editor altogether ;)

DEMO FILE:
drupal-milne-feed-test.html

MAIN SCRIPT:
drupal-milne-news-feed.js

DEPENDENCIES:
vue.min.js
vue-resource.min.js

CSS:
drupal-milne-news-feed.css

DEMO URL:
http://eres.geneseo.edu/libraryhours/drupal-milne-feed-test.html




